        <script type="text/javascript">
         var screenWidth = $(window).width();
     var activeComponent = $("#athleteBox");
     var slideIndex = 1;
 
     $('div.services').click(function () {
 
         
         //Reset all buttons
         var allDivs = $("#contentMenu").children("div");
         for (var i=0; i<allDivs.length;i++) {
             var l = $(allDivs[i]).children("a");
             var e = $(l[0]).children("em");
             var im = $(e[0]).children("img");
             $(im[0]).removeClass("image-hover");
             $(im[1]).addClass("image-hover");
         }
         
 
         var lnk = $(this).children("a");
         var newObj = $(lnk[0]).attr("data-obj");
 
         var ems = $(lnk[0]).children("em");
         var imgs = $(ems[0]).children("img");
         
         //Highlight the active button
         if (imgs.length == 2)
         {
             $(imgs[0]).addClass("image-hover");
             $(imgs[1]).removeClass("image-hover");
         }
 
 
 
         if (newObj != activeComponent) {
 
             $(activeComponent).animate(
                 {   left: '-2000px'}, 
                 {   duration:2000, 
                     //easing: 'easeOutBack',
                     complete: function () {
                         $(this).css('left', '2000px');
                         $(this).appendTo('#container');
                         //$(this).html("<img src='images/loading.gif' />");
                     }
                 });
             //var leftPos = (screenWidth - 950) / 2;
             var leftPos = 0;
             activeComponent = newObj;
             $(newObj).animate(
                 {   left: leftPos },
                 {   duration:1000//, 
                     //easing: 'easeOutBounce'
                 });
 
             if ($(newObj).html().length < 100)
                 $(newObj).load($(newObj).attr("data-page"));
         }
     });
 
     function querystring(key) {
         var re = new RegExp('(?:\\?|&)' + key + '=(.*?)(?=&|$)', 'gi');
         var r = [], m;
         while ((m = re.exec(document.location.search)) != null) r.push(m[1]);
         return r;
     }
 
     $(function () {
 
         //var leftPos = (screenWidth - 950) / 2;
         var leftPos = 0;
 
         var page = querystring("page");
         if (page != "" && page != null) {
             activeComponent = $("#" + page + "Box");
             $(activeComponent).animate(
                            { left: leftPos },
                            {
                                duration: 'slow',
                                easing: 'easeOutBounce',
                            });
             $(activeComponent).load("pages/" + page + ".aspx");
         }
         else {
             $(activeComponent).animate(
                             { left: leftPos },
                             {
                                 duration: 'slow',
                                 easing: 'easeOutBounce',
                             });
             $(activeComponent).load("pages/athletes.aspx");
         }
 
         
 
          
          window.setInterval(slideEventUp, 8000);
 
     });
     $(window).resize(function() {
       screenWidth = $(window).width();
         //var leftPos = (screenWidth - 950) / 2;
       var leftPos = 0;
         $(activeComponent).css("left", leftPos + "px");
     });
 
     function slideEventUp() {
         
         var topLocation = slideIndex * 120;
 
         $('#upEvents').animate(
                 {   top: -topLocation },
                 {   duration:1200, 
                     easing: 'easeOutBounce',
                 });
         slideIndex += 1;
         if (slideIndex > 17)
             slideIndex = 0;
         //setInterval(slideEventUp(), 4000);
     }
        </script>
